title: Ebro In The Morning - Nems Joins the Program + White-Ish Wednesday

itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 3/23/2022.

Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio discussing everything under the sun and playing White Ish Wednesday! Plus Nems joins the Program. 

Get excited for the gurus to help solve your problems and get the latest news with Flashing Lights. All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
